      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "YAPPING ACES (2) was strongly fancied latest and proved too good with a 1.5 lengths win at this track in a handy 16.62. Fair draw can see a good run and likes the trip. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from three attempts. Can continue on her winning ways. ZARA'S COMET (8) was well in the market last time but only managed fourth (16.83), beaten 2.5 lengths. Was in the money the start prior. Shapes as one to consider. LUCY BURROW (1) has been a little hard to follow, finishing out of the placings latest but was in winning form two back scoring in a Grade 6 at this track. Expecting sharp improvement this line-up.",
